op working -->\r\nTwo extensions were added to allow a user to enable showing line numbers and line endings.\r\n\r\nThe line numbers extension uses the built-in extension from codemirror.\r\n\r\nThe line ending extension adds a pilcrow widget which is enabled along with the `Highlight Whitespace` setting. It adds a DOM element at the end of each line.~~assigns a CSS class which shows the pilcrow at the end of lines. The CSS was adapted from the one in the documentation to not show a newline when a pilcrow is on a blank line.~~\r\n\r\n## Additional information\r\n<!-- If there is anything else that might be of interest, please provide it here -->\r\n\r\n<img width=\"917\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-22 at 14 16 17\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a88b9ba5-b29e-473e-ae4c-d419ced668ae\" />\r\n\r\n<!-- Please provide any testing system -->\r\nTested on: <!-- OS including version -->\r\n"}, "closed_issues": [], "merged_at": null, "merge_commits": [], "RANK": 1, "COUNT": 6}]}}